metadata.name: A Kid Called Rug
metadata.description: This NFT collection is a satirical work and should not be taken seriously. Any resemblance to a real person or entity named Rugsby is purely coincidental and unintentional. The purpose of this collection is to provide a humorous commentary on the current state of the NFT market, and should not be interpreted as any sort of endorsement or criticism of any real-world individual or group.
